Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4月15日  『日照良好』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要想去做  早起之類的也是做得到的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長好像還沒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對校長保密喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野屋老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止對你發了不少火  真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後還請你自由隨意地  竭盡所能大膽發揮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四  二…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做早操了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮  你也要來一起做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  感覺能舒展筋骨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃  小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵醒…你…了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容不燦爛點可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得不夠甜美的話  是會被扣分的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在睡著呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天結束啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師們好像下午要開會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去後要做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先去吃完午飯再說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去食堂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有沒有空位啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去買飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃學姐  宮子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選了豬排飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正要去買飯  要一起吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和同班的同學一起吃  已經幫我佔好位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那薺殿下呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  今天沒在學校看到她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊  這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薺已經先回去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？只有一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  快上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自一人回家真是少見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  只是東西忘在教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回教室取東西  所以晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…那就無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  你那說話方式…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那班級怎麼樣？能好好相處嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說怎麼樣…  沒什麼變化啊  又沒換班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就到這裡了  謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠陪我這一程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是順路而已  順路啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…明天見！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經做好出門的準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安  中午承蒙關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉  有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的  我想去買窗簾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道這附近哪裡有賣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗簾…哪裡有賣呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英學姐和尋學姐出門了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薺的話  可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦  小薺是本地人呢	
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（「ジモティー」俗語，意為本地人。）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基莫提？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義大利人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗簾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有沒有什麼推薦的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「I'm home」應該不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「I'm home」是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…就是類似綜合性超市的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有賣各種各樣的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  賣各種各樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有平底鍋  垃圾袋  廚櫃  螺絲  花盆等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有精靈先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  還讓你陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店的位置口頭上很難說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問下  我們也能一起去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉  你這段時期窗簾是怎麼弄的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用的是從家裡帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但長度不合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很在意的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃親  躲進那邊的窗簾裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要偷東西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30厘米  和剛才的加起來總長是180厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  真是麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思  一百日元的捲尺真是太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃學姐  能過來一點嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠量出來耶  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經認不出路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英學姐來短信說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「現在正在逛畫具店  有什麼想要的東西嗎？」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這畫具店是哪裡的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在鄰鎮大型百貨商場裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薺知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  雖然沒進去過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的畫具店很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我也去瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天上了吉野屋老師的課
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是素描課
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野屋老師還說要當模特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「只要大家開口  要老師裸體都行！」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她是吉野屋老師嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒穿奇怪的服裝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就換上了輕飄飄的那種衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過被校長發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是太悲劇了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算躲到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡  「I'm home」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「基莫提」人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那種人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像能做出些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「什麼」是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是安全帽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種專業物品光看看就會感覺很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「I'm home」真不是蓋的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾的種類很齊全呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是也買些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也想要些小毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是鏈鋸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種規格應有盡有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很有趣呢  小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伐木工？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  有好多筆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是不怎麼想邁腿前進呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微去下洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就在這裡等你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷場了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為學姐的我得想點辦法才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時候如果是少女漫畫的話會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  乃莉佩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗簾的顏色還是準備選藍色系的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了～平時總是不自覺地選藍色系的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次想選個不一樣的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我有說過我喜歡藍色系的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身邊不是有很多藍色系的東西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮子學姐真是個奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還沒到窗簾專賣區的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由得就拿了很多東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉  要用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薺各式各樣的都買了些什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…礦泉水  潤唇膏  柔軟劑  膠帶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有毛巾和電池
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘是些隨處可買到的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到窗簾專賣區了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,種類真不少呢  真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備買張蕾絲窗簾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  今天就只買普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  由乃親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾絲女王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮  那身裝扮看起來就像是個新娘似的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願意宣誓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薺  你覺得哪個比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與…與其問我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去問由乃學姐和宮子學姐是不是更…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既不是美術科
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也談不上什麼審美…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得你那種想法很片面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是說進了美術科就會全都有很好的審美感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才進美術科來學習的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審美不就是需要慢慢磨練的東西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不容分說地擅自認為有沒有審美感不是很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的話  應該會選這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛  就選這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就這麼決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  貌似決定了呢  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  不要偷偷摸摸地往這邊看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是房東吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房東也來買東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  想種些什麼東西試試呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來  暖陽莊也有個院子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  大家一起來種點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭菜園可是很有趣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜園…能收穫蔬菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能多一個配菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼做吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼草率地決定沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像會很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  能健康茁壯地成長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起齊心合力加油做吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能也不錯呢  種得好的話也會很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  既然由大家來種的話  我就樂得清閒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果豐收的話就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是期待呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉助同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條舊的窗簾能給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以啦  是要用來做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我那房間沒有窗簾…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一年來你是怎麼過來的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮的房間是用的百葉窗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很少放下來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年夏天的時候弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼弄的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦  尋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沙英學姐她們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到齊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋學姐  那個大袋子裡的是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個？由於太貴了平時不怎麼買
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在車站前的藥店裡賣得超～便宜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  小薺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋學姐也是因為喜歡那個花紋才買的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是因為喜歡那個花紋才買的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還買了這個回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕃茄的幼苗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然覺得茄子和黃瓜也不錯的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是以表決的方式決定買蕃茄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很好嘛  就種種看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～我鏟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果累了的話就儘管說  我來換手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薺  我們去打水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這是小宮的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一～二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披薩～意麵～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義大利蔬菜濃湯  燉蕃茄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太心急了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:18:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞煩了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看看電視吧  晚飯還在做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯的話  我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  不留下來吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家的份都做進去了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋學姐的手藝可是沒的說的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就留下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋學姐  再搬一個桌子來比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  這次有六個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去拿我房間裡的那張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃親  我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.41,0:19:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}請大家看這個玄關
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這玄關都和我的家差不多大小了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:20:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真太棒了  尋學姐的手藝真的超讚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是否合你們胃口  嚐嚐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  不用客氣多吃點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋經常給我們做飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋可是無所不能的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知就讓媽媽教我馬鈴薯燉肉的做法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋學姐也能夠教你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我可以幫忙試味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  宮子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做的料理會一點點增加的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼過來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還完全習慣不了一個人住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還要上學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得真的是很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小薺的節奏慢慢習慣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有去過食堂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼明天一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去之前先碰下頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…鈴一響就在樓梯口見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薺還有乃莉她們  從今往後還有許多的事要做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過小薺她們倆肯定能相處得很融洽的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕃茄如果能豐收的話就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4月15日  『完』  待續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都說說女孩子會喜歡什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  吃飯！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.91,0:23:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃閃亮亮的飾品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有可愛的洋裝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.95,0:23:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油滿塞的栗子蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓冰淇淋甜點和熱呼呼的豆沙包
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.62,0:23:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好吃的東西吃了都是會發胖的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:23:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.59,0:24:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『4月20日  女生的感受』
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『1月31日  直言不諱』
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.14,0:24:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在山吹高中裡等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.96,0:24:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要來看哦
